flowchart TD
    Start([Customer Datang Ke Kedai]) --> Discuss[Perbincangan Masalah<br/>Laptop/PC/Printer]
    Discuss --> Agree{Customer Setuju<br/>Tinggalkan Barang?}
    
    Agree -->|Ya| QR[Technician Sediakan<br/>QR Code]
    QR --> Scan[Customer Scan & Masukkan Data:<br/>• Nama<br/>• No Telefon<br/>• Jenis Barang<br/>• Model<br/>• Tick T&C]
    
    Scan --> BotThanks[Bot Hantar:<br/>Terima kasih nama<br/>Barang akan dicek<br/>Update akan dihantar]
    
    BotThanks --> TechCheck[Technician Periksa<br/>Laptop/PC/Printer]
    TechCheck --> TechPrompt[Tech Prompt Bot:<br/>• Masalah<br/>• Harga Repair]
    
    TechPrompt --> BotQuote[Bot Hantar Quotation:<br/>Masalah + Harga]
    BotQuote --> WaitConfirm{Tunggu Customer<br/>Confirmation}
    
    WaitConfirm -->|No Response 1 Day| Remind1[Bot Hantar<br/>Reminder 1]
    Remind1 --> WaitConfirm
    
    WaitConfirm -->|No Response 20 Days| Remind2[Bot Hantar<br/>Reminder 2]
    Remind2 --> WaitConfirm
    
    WaitConfirm -->|No Response 30 Days| Remind3[Bot Hantar<br/>Reminder 3]
    Remind3 --> WaitConfirm
    
    WaitConfirm -->|Customer Reply| Decision{Customer<br/>Setuju?}
    
    Decision -->|Tak Setuju| BotReject[Bot Hantar:<br/>Boleh ambil semula<br/>laptop]
    BotReject --> CustResponse[Customer Bagi Tahu<br/>Bila Nak Ambil]
    CustResponse --> End1([Customer Ambil Barang])
    
    Decision -->|Setuju| BotApprove[Bot Hantar:<br/>Laptop akan dibaiki<br/>Tunggu update]
    
    BotApprove --> TechRepair[Technician Mula<br/>Repair]
    TechRepair --> TechProgress[Tech Prompt Bot:<br/>Gambar Progress<br/>Kerja Yang Dilakukan]
    
    TechProgress --> BotProgress[Bot Hantar:<br/>Update Progress<br/>+ Gambar]
    
    BotProgress --> TechComplete[Tech Prompt Bot:<br/>Gambar Laptop Siap]
    TechComplete --> BotComplete[Bot Hantar:<br/>• Gambar Laptop Siap<br/>• Invoice<br/>• Boleh Ambil]
    
    BotComplete --> CustPickup[Customer Datang<br/>Ambil & Payment]
    CustPickup --> TechUpdate[Tech Update Bot:<br/>Customer Ambil & Bayar]
    
    TechUpdate --> BotReview[Bot Hantar:<br/>Terima Kasih<br/>+ Link Review]
    BotReview --> End2([Selesai])
    
